data.description: Welcome home to 5418 Harefield Dr in Canterbury Farms! This 3-bedroom residence boasts 2 full baths and a convenient half bath, perfect for entertaining guests. Step inside to a spacious living area that flows into an inviting breakfast bar and eat-in kitchen, where you can enjoy meals and morning coffee with ease. Upstairs, a versatile loft area awaits, ideal for a quiet study or a cozy reading nook, offering a peaceful retreat within the home. The primary bedroom is generously sized, and each bedroom offers a walk-in closet. Don't miss the impressive custom-made shelving in one of the secondary bedrooms (Currently being used as a study/man cave) that will remain for new owners. A freshly painted exterior gives this home a crisp, welcoming appearance, while the recently replaced HVAC system and water heater contribute to year-round comfort and efficiency. Also, say goodbye to carpets as this home features tile and laminate flooring throughout, adding ease of maintenance. Located conveniently to area schools, Lackland Airforce Base, Southwest Research Institute, and the vibrant HWY 151 shopping and amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule a visit today.
